WEBVTT

00:00.755 --> 00:03.008
Previously on AMC's Mad Men...

00:03.823 --> 00:05.471
You stay away from her!
You hear me?

00:05.784 --> 00:07.720
Don, are you ever gonna call back
the American Cancer Society?

00:08.031 --> 00:09.609
They've tried you twice this morning.

00:10.816 --> 00:12.624
I'm not gonna run out of
here crying tomorrow.

00:18.903 --> 00:19.711
She's gone.

00:20.904 --> 00:21.727
I know.

00:22.063 --> 00:23.391
I think it's time for us to move.

00:23.720 --> 00:28.304
Meet me for dinner, in the open,
wherever I want, because...

00:28.968 --> 00:30.247
We can do that now.

